---
title: Pan-Seared Salmon with Honeydew-Cucumber Salsa & Watercress Salad
description: Forget what you know about salsa—this version turns your traditional tomato salsa upside-down with refreshing crunch, minty brightness, and subtle sweetness. Served atop flaky salmon and crispy roasted sweet potatoes, you’ll be pleasantly surprised with this unusual combination of flavors.
